The paper deals with automated decision-making and learning from data, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of probabilistic models and reasoning also suggests a connection to robotics (cs.RO) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Finally, the experiments involve human judgement and decision-making, which could be relevant to cognitive science (cs.CY).
